text: Louis Kniep (April 10, 1876 - February 22, 1967) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1876 births Category:1967 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from New Jersey
